A LITTLE SHIMMER

Bold statement cuff bracelets sit alongside delicate, romantic earrings and timeless pendant necklaces: Chlo jewelry runs the gamut from timeless refinement to striking modernity. Updated every season, the collection embraces a natural spirit with baroque freshwater pearls, semi-precious stones and hand-blown glass details, not to mention hand-wrapped leather trim and deadstock silk ribbon. Polished gold brass infuses the pieces with a fine jewelry spirit that truly elevates the artful craftsmanship.
